p.k: The kids find out Dad has been dressing as a woman. / Darwin is delighted when they discover their old childhood toys, but soon realises that some things are best left in the past. / Join the citizens of Elmore for a song and dance spectacular that will have you covering your ears with joy. / The Wattersons will do whatever it takes to get into the first screening of the latest Stellar Odyssey sequel. / Richard decides that his work around the house is underappreciated by Nicole and goes on strike to prove it.
